comment: The signature-permutation of the automorphism which is derived from the first non-recursive automorphism *A069770 with recursion schema DEEPEN (see A122283 for the definition), or equivalently, derived from the 21st non-recursive automorphism *A089863 with recursion schema FORK (see A122201 for the definition).
